ot.com/2012/12/happy-christmas-merry-holidays-from.html";s:11:"author_name";s:4:"Yost";s:10:"author_uri";s:51:"http://www.blogger.com/profile/09715437509940349084";s:12:"author_email";s:19:"noreply@blogger.com";}i:18;a:12:{s:2:"id";s:59:"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-17480875.post-8230480446647097023";s:9:"published";s:29:"2012-12-11T16:00:00.001-05:00";s:7:"updated";s:29:"2012-12-11T16:00:18.108-05:00";s:5:"title";s:32:"No Bowl But New Streets in C-bus";s:12:"atom_content";s:980:"Sorry for the light posting.&nbsp; Just trying to wrap up everything for the end of the year.&nbsp; Ah, real life.<br /><br />Thankfully, our pal Surrounded in Columbus is always good for a nugget or four from deep behind enemy lines.&nbsp; Today he sent the picture below with the following email:<br /><br /><blockquote class="tr_bq"><i>Most people would be disappointed to be 12-0 &amp; staying home.&nbsp; They're not most people.</i></blockquote><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-I5Z0F58ILu8/UMeeQOm79OI/AAAAAAAADQc/9pZxMld-CSg/s1600/Columbus-20121211-00015.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="300" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-I5Z0F58ILu8/UMeeQOm79OI/AAAAAAAADQc/9pZxMld-CSg/s400/Columbus-20121211-00015.jpg" width="400" /></a></div><br />No word yet on when Tressel Boned Us But We Still Hoisted Him on Our Shoulders Like Morons Lane is going up.";s:12:"link_replies";s:150:"http://michiganzone.blogspot.com/feeds/8230480446647097023/comments/defaulthttp://www.blogger.com/comment.g?blogID=17480875&postID=8230480446647097023";s:9:"link_edit";s:71:"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/17480875/posts/default/8230480446647097023";s:9:"link_self";s:71:"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/17480875/posts/default/8230480446647097023";s:4:"link";s:78:"http://michiganzone.blogspot.com/2012/12/no-bowl-but-new-streets-in-c-bus.html";s:11:"author_name";s:4:"Yost";s:10:"author_uri";s:51:"http://www.blogg